<H2><font color=purple><i>The ICDT Council</i></font></H2>
<p>
In 1998, an international body, the ICDT Council, was formed. Its
tasks include various aspects of sponsoring and encouraging research
in database theory and related fields in Europe. Of primary importance among
these tasks is the organization of the ICDT.
The Council works in cooperation with EDBT (Extending Database
technology), the European organization
for database research that is responsible for the organization of the
biennial conference EDBT.



